Al Rosen (actor) https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Al_Rosen_(actor) 0 Albert Rosen (May 9, 1910 – August 2, 1990) was an American actor. He is known for his recurring role of "Al" in the television sitcom Cheers. Albert_Rosen ( May_9_,_1910 – August_2 , 1990 ) was an_American_actor .
